          "text": "来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘智远上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君子生平志不平，掌中无剑怎杀人？伸手要取天边月，只恨足下不生云。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，姓刘名高字智远，乃延安人氏。在总爷营中，当了一名火头军。闻听总爷"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呼唤，不知为了何事？待吾进帐，问个明白。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "报，刘高告进，参见总爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，少爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳彦真、岳存训",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唤小人进帐，有何吩咐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳彦真",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你家少爷，要在中途抢亲，无人保护。今欲命你前去，你可有此胆量？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人有此胆量。"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳彦真",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然如此，就命你前去，一路之上，须要小心在意。倘若抢得亲回，本镇定有"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳彦真",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "重赏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢总爷提拔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳彦真",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只是一件。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪一件？"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳彦真",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此番前去，万万不可杀人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（岳存训摇手。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（岳彦真下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但不知少爷几时起程？"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳存训",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此事不可迟延，即刻起程。与爷带马！"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳存训",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "帐中奉了爹爹命，"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳存训",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "去至中途要抢亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳存训",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "但愿此去把功成。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（岳存训、刘智远同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "岳彦真→岳存训",
          "turns": 5
        },
        {
