    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "刘智远",
        "岳存训"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖水底鱼〗。刘智远上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住！想我临行之时，总爷叫道：此番抢亲，不许杀人。我若不杀人，这亲事"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "焉能到手？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（岳存训上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳存训",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘高，亲事不能到手，如何是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳呀少爷吓！我家总爷，不许我杀人。若不杀人，这亲事是怎能到手？"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳存训",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘高，你只管杀人。有你少爷替你担待！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，你就闪开了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四下手、二英雄、四青袍、朱文杰同上，同起打。刘智远杀朱文杰，夺花轿同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
