    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "刘智远",
        "岳存训",
        "岳彦真"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（岳彦真上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳彦真",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "旌旗不住空中摆，"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳彦真",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "本镇坐守在潼台。"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳彦真",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "三、六、九日把兵排。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（岳存训上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳存训",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且将抢亲事，进帐说端的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳存训",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见爹爹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳彦真",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿少礼，一旁坐下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳存训",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢爹爹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳彦真",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿进帐，有何军情？"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳存训",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可恨朱温，霸占了孩儿的亲事。孩儿意欲在中途路上前去抢亲，不知爹爹意下"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳存训",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳彦真",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿前去，无人保护，为父放心不下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳存训",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我营中有一火头军，名唤刘高，此人颇有胆量。若命此人前去，保定孩儿，料"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳存训",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "然无事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳彦真",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿将他唤进帐来，待为父看过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳存训",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳存训",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘高进帐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘智远上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君子生平志不平，掌中无剑怎杀人？伸手要取天边月，只恨足下不生云。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，姓刘名高字智远，乃延安人氏。在总爷营中，当了一名火头军。闻听总爷"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呼唤，不知为了何事？待吾进帐，问个明白。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "报，刘高告进，参见总爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，少爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳彦真、岳存训",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唤小人进帐，有何吩咐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳彦真",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你家少爷，要在中途抢亲，无人保护。今欲命你前去，你可有此胆量？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人有此胆量。"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳彦真",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然如此，就命你前去，一路之上，须要小心在意。倘若抢得亲回，本镇定有"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳彦真",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "重赏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢总爷提拔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳彦真",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只是一件。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪一件？"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳彦真",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此番前去，万万不可杀人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（岳存训摇手。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘智远",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（岳彦真下。）"
        }
      ],
